        <mxCell id="design-text" value="&lt;span style='font-size:10px;color:#495057'&gt;1. Pipeline shortens at each hop: [DN2,DN3] -&gt; [DN3] -&gt; []&lt;br&gt;2. ACK bubbles from tail to head, Client gets ACK only after all replicas written&lt;br&gt;3. Each chunk = one brpc request-response (no streaming)&lt;br&gt;4. Client egress bandwidth = 1x data; replication bandwidth distributed across DataNodes&lt;/span&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;" vertex="1" parent="1">
